{
  "stem": "17625.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 136.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the crematoriums and all, all the, the, the, the-- they built new bunkers and then they-- then they-- and before that, before the Hungrians, they took and a few hundred [INAUDIBLE], fresh ones, maybe 400 on top of this.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then came a selection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the selection-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I'll go back a little bit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Kaminski was, was, was kapo on Crematorium 2.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that time, I, I, I didn't finish what I-- what I-- what I finished there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't convince the camp to do anything, to do it, because they, they put it off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The time was playing for them, because the Russians came nearer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Lublin was already-- at that time was already in the hands of, of, of Norway or, or, or they [? coming in ?].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The war turned around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] how do I want to say-- sonderkommando went on their own.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- to tell you the truth, I was not in this politics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I don't-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There, there, there are people who were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't take me into, into, to those things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one day, comes a special shipment-- a, a special car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us, the whole kommando of Crematorium 5, and put this in the-- in the-- in the-- in the inside not to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They close us up, and they did their own work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What they did is they took out Kaminski from, from, from Crematorium 1-- 2, and they burned him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had something, some smell, that something was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they watched us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was '44.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The middle of '44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
